title: **4 WEEKS FREE** Immediate Move-Ins Available! Beautiful 1 BED/1 BATH
posting_body: ['**4 WEEKS FREE** !!', 'Immediate Move-Ins Available!!', '*Beautiful Studio*', 'Everything you need for balanced living, with both apartment home and community-wide amenities designed to enhance your sense of well-being as well as your desire to connect with others.', 'One, two, and three bedroom apartment homes located in Aurora, Colorado.', 'Amenties:', '-Access to Denvers 53 Acre Park System', '-Side-by-side refrigerators with water dispenser in door', '-Granite countertops with tile backsplashes', '-Pool courtyard with infinity edge, resort-style pool including tanning ledge, hot tub and pool bar; outdoor kitchen with both grilling stations and a smoker; ample sitting and lounging areas, plus fire feature', '-Fitness Center with Yoga-Cardio Room', '-Contemporary cabinetry', '-Combination Shower/Bath*', '-Pet Friendly', '-USB Outlets', '-Mudrooms', '-Fitness center with cardio and strength equipment and a movement studio featuring both yoga and spin cycles', 'Call or Text Tyler to set up your for Fast Personal Showings or Virtual Showings!', '*Restrictions Apply.', 'Pricing, availability and lease terms subject to change anytime!']
